data.description:
PAY NO PROPERTY TAXES FOR 10 YEARS ON THESE BEAUTIFUL NEW BUILDS!! This home is one of four beautifully designed new builds in the highly sought after Pendleton Heights neighborhood. This upper east side neighborhood is just blocks away from the finest downtown attractions. This home boasts an entertainers dream with a large covered front porch and rear patio. The open floor plan reveals a beautifully designed kitchen featuring a beautiful quartz island, quartz countertops, gorgeous custom solid maple cabinets, and stainless appliances. The first floor also hosts a mudroom with laundry included. The second floor consists of the master suite and gorgeous bath featuring a double vanity with custom cabinetry as well. Upstairs also includes two other bedrooms and bath. This fully finished basement has an oversized bedroom, bath, family room, and storm or wine cellar. AND PAY NO PROPERTY TAXES FOR 10 YEARS!!!! THAT'S HUGE!!! 
AI virtual staging was used in some of these photos.
